---
import Layout from '../../layouts/SlideShow.astro';
---
<Layout title="Slide 6">
    <main class="p-8 w-full h-full grid grid-rows-[auto_1fr]">
        <section class="flex justify-left items-center">
            <h1 class="text-8xl">Scamming: No Risk All The Reward</h1>
        </section>
        <section class="p-4 grid gap-12 grid-cols-2 text-3xl">
            <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <p class="text-6xl text-slide-darkgreen">Australia</p>
                <div class="h-full flex flex-col justify-evenly">
                    <p>
                        Losses to scams 2020 - May 2022<br>
                        <span class="text-slide-darkgreen">$755 Hundred Million</span> | <span class="text-slide-purple">RM2.2 Billion</span>
                    </p>
                    <p> 
                        Population of 25.69 million<br>
                        <span class="text-slide-darkgreen">$29.38</span> | <span class="text-slide-purple">RM85.63</span> Per Person
                    </p>
                    <p>28,707 scams were reported in 2022</p>
                    <p>72% of the businesses surveyed reported experiencing a cyber incident</p>
                    <p class="text-center">
                        Solution Focus
                        <ul class="ml-auto mr-auto text-left">
                            <li>1. Hardware/Software 59%</li>
                            <li>2. Budget 56%</li>
                            <li>3. Training 52%</li>
                            <li>6. Hire specialist 42%</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <p class="text-6xl text-slide-purple">Malaysia</p>
                <div class="h-full flex flex-col justify-evenly">
                    <p>
                        Losses to scams 2020 - May 2022<br>
                        <span class="text-slide-purple">RM5.2 Billion</span> | <span class="text-slide-darkgreen">$1.7 Billion</span>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Population of 33.57 million<br>
                        <span class="text-slide-purple">RM154.90</span> | <span class="text-slide-darkgreen">$51.51</span> Per Person
                    </p>
                    <p>In 2022, scams made up 71% (5,219) of attacks</p>
                    <p>76% of the businesses surveyed reported experiencing a cyber incident</p>
                    <p class="text-center">
                        Solution Focus
                        <ul class="ml-auto mr-auto text-left">
                            <li>1. Monitoring 83%</li>
                            <li>2. Move to Cloud 78%</li>
                            <li>3. Budget 77%</li>
                            <li>8. Hire specialist 49%</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>